  "title": "ISic001169. Funerary inscription to Attikon",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\n                    Ἀγαθίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\"><span data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἀττίκων\">Ἀττίκων</span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\"><span data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγαθίνος\">Ἀγ̣αθίνου</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἀττίκων\">Ἀττίκων</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγαθίνος\">Ἀγαθίνου</span>  <span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">χαῖρε</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa, Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\n                    Ἀγαθίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\"><span data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἀττίκων\">ΑΤΤΙΚΩΝ</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\"><span data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγαθίνος\">Α.ΑΘΙΝΟΥ</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Ἀττίκων\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Ἀττίκων\">ΑΤΤΙΚΩΝ</span><span data-text=\"Ἀγαθίνου\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἀγαθίνος\">ΑΓΑΘΙΝΟΥ</span><span data-text=\"χαῖρε\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"χαίρω\">ΧΑΙΡΕ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001169_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001169_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001169.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001169-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text from autopsy</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>Previous editions do not recognise the gamma on line 2 as being almost entirely obscured</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou</a></p>  <p>Attikon, son of Agathinos, farewell.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The name Attikon is unique. The name Agathinos, is not particularly frequent, and this is its first attestation in Sicily.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Manni Piraino 1971 186 no.2 tav.55.2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001774\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001774</a>  </li><li> Brugnone 1974 8 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001397\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001397</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>All alphas have a broken mid-bar, and the omega in line 1 is tear-drop shaped. Serifs used on most letters. Some irregular spacing between letters, particularly in line 1 between the kappa and omega. Upsilon in line 2 is very long.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Θ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Θ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Θ-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Θ type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ν-type1.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ν type1.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ο-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ο type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Τ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Τ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Υ-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Υ type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ω-type2.2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ω type2.2.1</a> </p> Line 1  25-30  Line 2  21-26 (upsilon 36)  Line 3  21-30  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
